										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="2"><strong>怎样才能挑到好吃更香甜的水果？10种水果的挑法，保你一挑一个准</strong></p>
<p>水果在我们日常生活中是不可缺少的，水果的好处很多，可以保持人体的营养均衡，还可以促进肠胃蠕动，对消化系统也有好处。水果中含有多种维生素，多吃水果可以延缓衰老，可以使皮肤变得很光滑。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-739" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c1fce6570c9bb4c1373b474a44c4d1ec-1024x674.jpg" width="1024" height="674" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c1fce6570c9bb4c1373b474a44c4d1ec-1024x674.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c1fce6570c9bb4c1373b474a44c4d1ec-300x198.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c1fce6570c9bb4c1373b474a44c4d1ec-768x506.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c1fce6570c9bb4c1373b474a44c4d1ec.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>水果的好处虽然很多，但是口感也很重要，所以我们在购买时挑出好吃的水果也很重要，下面给大家整理了一套挑选水果的秘籍，保你一挑一个准，就连水果店的老板都得佩服你。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-740" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/529234f592b21009edc3944bb10b84dc-1024x574.jpg" width="1024" height="574" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/529234f592b21009edc3944bb10b84dc-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/529234f592b21009edc3944bb10b84dc-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/529234f592b21009edc3944bb10b84dc-768x431.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/529234f592b21009edc3944bb10b84dc.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="3">1、火龙果</h1>
<p data-track="40">我们挑选火龙果时要拿在手上掂一下，<strong>越重的火龙果越好，汁多果肉饱满，果形选果肉比较均匀的。</strong>然后看颜色尽量选择红色部位多的，如果绿色的部分很绿说明火龙果是比较新鲜的，如果绿色的部位发黄说明已经放很长时间了<strong>。最后要注意不要选择瘦的，火龙果越胖越饱满说明成熟的越好，味道清甜很美味哦！</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-741" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3d76e0adefaf2c8eaa3b28cc275062d4-1024x587.jpg" width="1024" height="587" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3d76e0adefaf2c8eaa3b28cc275062d4-1024x587.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3d76e0adefaf2c8eaa3b28cc275062d4-300x172.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3d76e0adefaf2c8eaa3b28cc275062d4-768x440.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3d76e0adefaf2c8eaa3b28cc275062d4.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="5">2、山竹</h1>
<p data-track="39">大家都知道<strong>新鲜的山竹要先看它的蒂，如果是绿色说明这个山竹的冷藏时间不会太长，还算比较新鲜。</strong>个头尽量选择中等不大不小的，用手轻轻地捏一下，如果外壳比较柔软，并且有弹性，很容易就打开了，说明果肉是好的已经成熟，里面的果肉是纯白色的，这种山竹的口感也不会差。如果外壳特别硬很难捏开，多半是放置久了已经坏掉了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-742" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b33ddf12ae5f25997c2b5507ff7a01e6.jpg" width="555" height="431" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b33ddf12ae5f25997c2b5507ff7a01e6.jpg 555w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/b33ddf12ae5f25997c2b5507ff7a01e6-300x233.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 555px) 100vw, 555px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-743" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/70059e81dded037df19037606ba44309.jpg" width="648" height="431" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/70059e81dded037df19037606ba44309.jpg 648w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/70059e81dded037df19037606ba44309-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="38">山竹不利于存放建议大家随吃随买。<strong>最后我们看山竹底部的瓣，有多少个花瓣就说明有多少瓣果肉，当然是花瓣越多越好哦！</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-744" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/80cae6cdaccc5d664d028e8eac57af4e-845x1024.jpg" width="845" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/80cae6cdaccc5d664d028e8eac57af4e-845x1024.jpg 845w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/80cae6cdaccc5d664d028e8eac57af4e-248x300.jpg 248w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/80cae6cdaccc5d664d028e8eac57af4e-768x931.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/80cae6cdaccc5d664d028e8eac57af4e.jpg 1056w" sizes="(max-width: 845px) 100vw, 845px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="7">3、榴莲</h1>
<p data-track="37">购买榴莲首先看外表是否饱满匀称，然后看它的皮薄与厚，<strong>然后看颜色榴莲要选颜色偏黄的，一般黄色的会比较熟，口感吃起来会特别的甜糯。</strong>然后再看榴莲的刺，刺大的榴莲果肉饱满，刺小的榴莲没有长开，里面肉特别少。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-745" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/678ada9dac0ffc783b556cfcd081372e-1024x575.jpg" width="1024" height="575" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/678ada9dac0ffc783b556cfcd081372e-1024x575.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/678ada9dac0ffc783b556cfcd081372e-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/678ada9dac0ffc783b556cfcd081372e-768x431.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/678ada9dac0ffc783b556cfcd081372e.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="9">4、西瓜</h1>
<p data-track="36">首先看西瓜头部的瓜藤，我们购买的<strong>西瓜瓜藤旁边一般都会有个须，如果这个须是有点干的说明是长熟的西瓜，如果须是青的建议大家别购买，多半只有5成熟左右，口感肯定不会太甜的。</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-746" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4a34659bd17e65a5cdc2ef30135b241-842x1024.jpg" width="842" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4a34659bd17e65a5cdc2ef30135b241-842x1024.jpg 842w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4a34659bd17e65a5cdc2ef30135b241-247x300.jpg 247w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4a34659bd17e65a5cdc2ef30135b241-768x934.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4a34659bd17e65a5cdc2ef30135b241.jpg 1052w" sizes="(max-width: 842px) 100vw, 842px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="35">然后看纹路，纹路如果不均匀，还出现段纹这种瓜建议不要买。然后看西瓜的肚脐部位，<strong>建议选择脐部小的，挑选出的这种西瓜皮薄还特别甜，如果西瓜脐部大并且皮还厚，这种西瓜的果肉会比较少并且口感很差。</strong>最后我们用听声音来判断，声音听起来很清脆嘭嘭的可以购买，如果拍出的声音很闷，听起来当当的建议别购买这种瓜。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-747" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/47b21ab48a79ebdef7cc47200aa4553c-1024x573.jpg" width="1024" height="573" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/47b21ab48a79ebdef7cc47200aa4553c-1024x573.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/47b21ab48a79ebdef7cc47200aa4553c-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/47b21ab48a79ebdef7cc47200aa4553c-768x430.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/47b21ab48a79ebdef7cc47200aa4553c.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="11">5、苹果</h1>
<p data-track="34">买苹果主要选红富士，<strong>红富士分全红和条红两种品质，条红是短枝红富士，全红是长枝，同地区的情况下，条红的含糖量更高，汁水也多，酸度刚刚好</strong>。全红的苹果只是好看而已，还有一点苹果的好坏和套袋没有什么关系，果农套袋的目的主要是为了防虫和果面光滑，<strong>即使光照得再好，条红的苹果也不会变成全红的，条红苹果虽然卖相一般，但是吃起来口感确实是最好的。</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-748" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/607b2b550adcf3876af7b94ba3fd46d6-1024x587.jpg" width="1024" height="587" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/607b2b550adcf3876af7b94ba3fd46d6-1024x587.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/607b2b550adcf3876af7b94ba3fd46d6-300x172.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/607b2b550adcf3876af7b94ba3fd46d6-768x440.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/607b2b550adcf3876af7b94ba3fd46d6.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="13">6、芒果</h1>
<p data-track="33">挑选芒果一定要选<strong>看起来比较圆润、饱满一些的</strong>，<strong>颜色发黄看起来比较纯正的，摸起来不软不硬，离很远都能闻到香味的。</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-749" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/9fb1ebfa4895a85508cae01948462d2b-1024x569.jpg" width="1024" height="569" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/9fb1ebfa4895a85508cae01948462d2b-1024x569.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/9fb1ebfa4895a85508cae01948462d2b-300x167.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/9fb1ebfa4895a85508cae01948462d2b-768x427.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/9fb1ebfa4895a85508cae01948462d2b.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>尽量挑选7成熟以上的，这样买回去存放一天左右就可以吃了。如果买熟透的芒果先看芒果的蒂部，如果外皮皱起就说明水分已经快没了，芒果如果没有完全熟口感就会酸、涩会非常难吃。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-750" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/378aa83957bca0e08605cbe2c88c1264-1024x497.jpg" width="1024" height="497" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/378aa83957bca0e08605cbe2c88c1264-1024x497.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/378aa83957bca0e08605cbe2c88c1264-300x146.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/378aa83957bca0e08605cbe2c88c1264-768x373.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/378aa83957bca0e08605cbe2c88c1264.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="15">7、桃子</h1>
<p data-track="32">桃子首先要选母桃，<strong>就是桃子上面没有尖的，有尖的桃子非常难吃</strong>，圆头地吃起来才又大又甜。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-751" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a4fce05ccb81d59c56646fa206548960-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a4fce05ccb81d59c56646fa206548960-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a4fce05ccb81d59c56646fa206548960-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a4fce05ccb81d59c56646fa206548960-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/a4fce05ccb81d59c56646fa206548960.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="31"><strong>母桃子色泽粉红，皮特别薄，尤其是熟透后的桃子特别好剥皮。其次就是闻香味，离好远都能够闻到香味的桃子是不会差的，个头要选择饱满均匀的，表皮光滑没有斑点的桃子</strong>。最后我们来看重量，拿在手里掂一下，比较重的桃子水分会比较多，口感更香甜。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-752" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/64578cfd1e6125da1221264c4b20f3a6-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/64578cfd1e6125da1221264c4b20f3a6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/64578cfd1e6125da1221264c4b20f3a6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/64578cfd1e6125da1221264c4b20f3a6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/64578cfd1e6125da1221264c4b20f3a6.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="17">8、石榴</h1>
<p data-track="30">挑选石榴首先看外形，如果外形是圆滚滚的说明还没有完全熟透，<strong>四方形的石榴才是真正长熟的。</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-753" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/99e0b6902b3c79d268c51affc42936f8-1024x685.jpg" width="1024" height="685" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/99e0b6902b3c79d268c51affc42936f8-1024x685.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/99e0b6902b3c79d268c51affc42936f8-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/99e0b6902b3c79d268c51affc42936f8-768x514.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/99e0b6902b3c79d268c51affc42936f8.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="29">然后看颜色，石榴颜色分黄、红、绿三种颜色，很多朋友都认为颜色鲜艳的红色石榴口感会更好，其实石榴的品种不同，<strong>黄色的石榴才是最甜的口感是最好的。还有最后一种分辨方法，石榴的底部如果是自然裂开的这种最好，很明显就是长熟的，果实比较饱满，口感更加香甜。</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-754" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4bcc90a1a3ed746f5bde3b61d67b144-1024x684.jpg" width="1024" height="684" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4bcc90a1a3ed746f5bde3b61d67b144-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4bcc90a1a3ed746f5bde3b61d67b144-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4bcc90a1a3ed746f5bde3b61d67b144-768x513.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d4bcc90a1a3ed746f5bde3b61d67b144.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="20">9、大枣</h1>
<p data-track="28">大枣挑选时首先不要看枣的外表，要看枣的饱满度，外皮没有裂痕的大枣。<strong>其次看枣的大小，选枣要选个头大一些的，大枣的果肉会比较厚，味道要比小枣口感更好。</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-755" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8441cf79738516753368753551190b67-1024x684.jpg" width="1024" height="684" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8441cf79738516753368753551190b67-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8441cf79738516753368753551190b67-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8441cf79738516753368753551190b67-768x513.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8441cf79738516753368753551190b67.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="27"><strong>然后再挑选比较有硬度的大枣，这种枣会很新鲜，口感不错，特别脆甜</strong>。挑选时可以摸一下，如果有破皮、凹陷的还有软一些的枣口都不是新鲜的，口感自然很差，所以挑选时一定要看清楚。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-756" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3124ffb3df859d004a1158c99b860237-1024x683.jpg" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3124ffb3df859d004a1158c99b860237-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3124ffb3df859d004a1158c99b860237-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3124ffb3df859d004a1158c99b860237-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/3124ffb3df859d004a1158c99b860237.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<h1 class="pgc-h-arrow-right" data-track="24">10、猕猴桃</h1>
<p>首先我们先看猕猴桃的外观，有些猕猴桃会使用膨大剂，用了膨大剂的猕猴桃果皮会非常的绿，膨大剂的浓度越大，猕猴桃的果身就很容易变粗，果实果肉的口感也不好。其次看猕猴桃表面的果毛，好的猕猴桃果毛是很难脱落下来的，如果果皮上的毛比较多，说明猕猴桃是很新鲜的，如果果毛易脱落还特别粗硬，就说明猕猴桃不够新鲜。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-757" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d801fb96c2980a3d7b94e39de7597c4d-1024x684.jpg" width="1024" height="684" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d801fb96c2980a3d7b94e39de7597c4d-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d801fb96c2980a3d7b94e39de7597c4d-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d801fb96c2980a3d7b94e39de7597c4d-768x513.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d801fb96c2980a3d7b94e39de7597c4d.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="25">然后看外观，<strong>猕猴桃不要选扁扁的，要选头部尖尖的</strong>。颜色接近土黄色日照比较充足的才会更甜。最后要看猕猴桃的大小，太小的猕猴桃成熟度不会太好，<strong>太大的猕猴桃口味反而会比较淡，选择中等大小的最好。</strong></p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-758" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/ddf572f3f538d291bf91875d109b9b91-1024x684.jpg" width="1024" height="684" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/ddf572f3f538d291bf91875d109b9b91-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/ddf572f3f538d291bf91875d109b9b91-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/ddf572f3f538d291bf91875d109b9b91-768x513.jpg 768w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/ddf572f3f538d291bf91875d109b9b91.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="26">所有的水果都会有一个共同点，<strong>只要是自然长熟的水果都会有股淡淡的果香味</strong>，而成熟度不够的水果几乎是闻不到的。最后再提醒一下大家很多网友认为有光泽和亮度的水果是好的，这样分辨是不正确的，现实中很多水果是经过人工打蜡的，打蜡的目的是为了保鲜存放时间更久。一般当季的水果很少用食用蜡来保鲜，进口水果和反季节的水果一般都会用食用蜡来保鲜，所以大家购买水果时一定要学会如何分辨。</p>
